375
00:32:26,340 --> 00:32:32,280
After His Majesty left, the precious historical records of the Divine-Devil War disappeared without a trace.

376
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:33,960
I can testify to that.

377
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:38,880
His Majesty has been either going in and out frequently or plotting with Yan Dan in the Yanxu Heavenly Palace.

378
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:42,600
I even saw them sleeping together.

379
00:32:45,380 --> 00:32:48,740
Qing Yun, what are you talking about?!

380
00:32:53,460 --> 00:32:55,260
Good for you, Ying Yuan.

381
00:32:55,260 --> 00:32:58,060
You laid low for 900 years just to find the Devil King.

382
00:32:58,060 --> 00:33:03,220
As soon as you returned, you were eager to destroy the evidence and pin the blame on His Supreme Majesty.

383
00:33:05,340 --> 00:33:07,880
The Asura Clan indeed cannot be trusted.

384
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:11,340
Kill him! Avenge our fellow immortals!

385
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:17,540
Emperor Ying Yuan, a remnant of the Asura Clan,

386
00:33:17,540 --> 00:33:20,860
